These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
3 different pets are kept: turtle, frog, hedgehog
There are 3 different favourite colors: emerald, purple, apricot
1. the person who likes purple is in the middle##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is the person who likes apricot##1
3. the owner of the turtle is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Pet   | turtle | frog | hedgehog   |
| Color      | emerald    | purple  | apricot |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
3 different games are played: billiard, backgammon, domino
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, azalea, sunflower
1. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person playing domino##1
2. the person who growsazalea is on the far left##1
3. the person who growsazalea is the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Game      | backgammon | billiard     | domino      |
| Flower   | azalea | daisy | sunflower |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, writing, drawing
3 different games are played: whist, poker, bridge
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person playing poker##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Hobby   | card-games | drawing  | writing       |
| Game       | whist     | poker | bridge |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: techno, country, disco
3 different pets are kept: dog, goat, cat
1. the fan of country is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
2. the fan of techno is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
3. the owner of the cat is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Music-Genre    | disco    | country     | techno |
| Pet   | cat | dog | goat     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different games are played: chess, mah-jongg, bridge
There are 3 different favourite colors: green, emerald, black
1. the person who likes emerald is the person playing bridge##1
2. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person playing chess##1
3. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person who likes green##1
4. the person playing chess is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Game         | mah-jongg | chess     | bridge |
| Color   | black        | green | emerald    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, poppy, iris
House: cottage, victorian, wooden
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the cottage house##1
2. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the victorian house##1
3. the person who growsiris is the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Flower        | iris | balloon-flower      | poppy  |
| House   | cottage       | victorian | wooden |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
3 different games are played: bridge, snooker, canasta
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, taxi, boat
1. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
2. the person playing snooker is the person driving the taxi##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Game   | canasta      | bridge     | snooker    |
| Transport           | helicopter | boat | taxi |

