There are 3 different nationalities: thai, turkish, pakistani
1. the turkish is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the pakistani##1
3. the person drinking tea is the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Beverage    | almond-milk | coffee | tea      |
| Nationality   | thai     | pakistani | turkish |

