.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-9::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, dahlia, tulip
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, fonseca, baccarat
1. the bongani-smoker is the person who growsdahlia##1
2. the fonseca-smoker is on the far right##1
3. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Flower   | tulip | dahlia | orchid  |
| Cigar     | baccarat     | bongani      | fonseca |

