There 3 different types of food: grapefruit, eggplant, cherry
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person eating grapefruit##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
3. the person eating cherry is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Pet   | lizard | guinea-pig   | goat  |
| Food   | cherry    | grapefruit | eggplant |

