There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, ebony, lavender
1. the software-developer is in the middle##1
2. the security-guard is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
3. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the software-developer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Job   | security-guard    | software-developer     | analyst   |
| Color   | ebony | brown | lavender |

