.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-13::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, bus, trike
3 different games are played: poker, canasta, mah-jongg
1. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person driving the trike is in the middle##1
3. the person playing poker is on the right of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1       |     2      |     3      |
| Transport   | roller     | trike   | bus     |
| Game    | mah-jongg | canasta | poker |

