.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-15::.
There 3 different types of food: watermelon, avocado, orange
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, tram, van
1. the person eating avocado is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the van is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
3. the person eating orange is on the right of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Food      | watermelon  | orange | avocado  |
| Transport   | tram | van   | motorbike |

