.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-16::.
City: hamburg, london, venice
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, nigerian, dutch
1. the nigerian is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
3. the person traveling to london is on the left of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |   3    |
| City   | london | hamburg | venice    |
| Nationality        | colombian    | dutch | nigerian |

