There 3 different types of food: onion, pepper, strawberry
1. the person eating strawberry is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far right##1
3. the person eating onion is the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |
| Beverage           | soy-milk | lemonade | almond-milk |
| Food   | strawberry  | onion      | pepper |

