.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
3 different games are played: go, scrabble, domino
The people have 3 different jobs:  software-developer, freelancer, architect
1. the freelancer is in the middle##1
2. the architect is on the left of the person playing go##1
3. the person playing scrabble is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Game    | domino | go       | scrabble  |
| Job   | architect  | freelancer | software-developer |

 